    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    High-Quality Material  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">At dbrand, we use only Authentic 3M vinyl on our Xbox One skins for the console and controller. That means, when you decide to take off your Xbox One wrap to put on a new one, there is never any adhesive residue left on your device. Guaranteed. We are committed to providing our customers with uncompromising quality. You can relax. We only use the highest grade materials on the planet.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/quality.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--xbox-one-precision taxonomy-term--device-features--precision">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content--2"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Unrivaled Precision  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">The pictures don't lie. Our Xbox One skins offer the most precise fit on the market. Only ACellShop offers a flawless cutout for the Xbox logo on the top of the console, plus we have an unmatched number of customization options at no extra cost. We've meticulously measured each of the cutouts on our skins for the Xbox One over a thousand times, down to the micro millimeter. It literally isn't possible to find a better fitting, higher quality Xbox One decal than the one you'll find at dbrand. We are the definition of precision.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/precision.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
<div class="taxonomy-term--device-features taxonomy-term--full taxonomy-term--device-features--full taxonomy-term taxonomy-term--xbox-one-variety taxonomy-term--device-features--variety">
    <div class="group group-content" id="taxonomy-term-device-features-full-group-content--3"><div class="group__inner"><div class="text-body">
  <h3 class="field field--name-title-field field--type-text field--label-hidden">
    Our Variety, Your Choice  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">Our Xbox One decals come in six true-textured finishes: Carbon Fiber, Brushed Titanium, Matte, Leather, powder-coated True Colour, and Wood. You won't find a more authentic texture among any of our competitors. Our wraps for the Xbox One controller and console are available in a custom-selected range of exclusive, textured materials. From black leather to gold, powder-coated red to matte white, even mahogany... you'll be sure to find one that matches your style.</div></div>
  <figure class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden">
    <img src="../sites/default/files/images/device-features/variety.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="" />  </figure>
</div></div></div>
